import sys

input = sys.stdin.readline

def main():
    N = int(input())
    D, X = map(int, input().split())
    A = [None] * N
    for i in range(N):
        A[i] = int(input())

    ans = X
    for a in A:
        q, r, = divmod(D - 1, a)
        ans += q + 1

    print(ans)

if __name__ == "__main__":
    main()

n = int(input())
li_a = list(map(int, input().split()))

li_aw = [0] + li_a + [0]

# 全ルートを回るコスト
total_cost = 0
for i in range(1, len(li_aw)):
    total_cost += abs(li_aw[i - 1] - li_aw[i])

for i in range(n):
    # li_aw上の取りやめポイントindex
    delete_index = i + 1
    delete_cost = abs(li_aw[delete_index - 1] - li_aw[delete_index]) + abs(li_aw[delete_index] - li_aw[delete_index + 1])
    add_cost = abs(li_aw[delete_index - 1] - li_aw[delete_index + 1])
    print(total_cost - delete_cost + add_cost)

import math

N = int(input())

spot = np.zeros(N + 1)
spot[1:] = np.array(list(map(int, input().split())))

    print(int(tot - math.fabs(spot[i] - spot[i-1]) - math.fabs(spot[(i+1) % (N+1)] - spot[i])\
